  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2021-04-29",
    "date": "2021-05-17T14:24:26Z",
    "text": "This resolution (1) expresses support for the designation of May 2021 as Motorcycle Safety Awareness Month; (2) recognizes the contribution of motorcycles to the transportation mix; (3) encourages motorcycle awareness by all road users; (4) recognizes that motorcyclists have a right to the road and that all motorists should safely share the roadways; (5) encourages rider safety education, training, and proper gear for safe motorcycle operation; and (6) supports the goals of Motorcycle Safety Awareness Month."
